{"tid":2366010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又話食黃店？龍門冰室河畔花園分店被指欠租　遭業主追23.1萬及交還舖位","createTime":"2021-01-14T07:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T17:09:39.000Z","uid":333488,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6136ba879bc296b03684ba5c550ddc915ed0070f","tid":2366010,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HyyxzAz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHyyxzAz.jpg&h=f22faced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n龍門冰室的沙田河畔花園分店涉拖欠租金，以及差餉和地租，約23.1萬元。該舖的業主昨（13日）入稟高等法院，向龍門冰室老闆張俊傑追討涉款，和要求對方交還舖位。<br />\n<br />\n原告為帝寶發展有限公司，被告為張俊傑。張俊傑去年中宣布，退出「黃色經濟圈」。<br />\n原告在入稟狀指，於去年3月和被告簽下3年租約，把沙田河畔花園的舖位，以月租18萬元租予被告，讓對方經營龍門冰室，被告另需支付差餉和地租等雜費。<br />\n惟被告拖欠去年12月的租金，以及去年6月至12月之間的差餉和地租，合共23.1萬多元。雖然原告透過律師發信追討，但不果，遂入稟追討。<br />\n案件編號：HCA58/2020<br />\n<br />\n哎&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cfacb86f8c0b18dbb85c5ea71f917fe13a5b86","tid":2366010,"uid":97,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:40:35.000Z","msg":"又迫害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99d5702da593ab08029e9a5207c361e94bef396","tid":2366010,"uid":333488,"like":12,"dislike":15,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"講真，啲嘢好撚難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9227f3891acf5b39bf854666acf001071dbae5","tid":2366010,"uid":39710,"like":16,"dislike":9,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d99d5702da593ab08029e9a5207c361e94bef396","tid":2366010,"uid":333488,"like":12,"dislike":15,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"講真，啲嘢好撚難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:52:21.000Z","msg":"好過好多茶餐廳啦"},{"pid":"24254317a44916be228e12a13f35b9283536281e","tid":2366010,"uid":176981,"like":11,"dislik